# ai-engineering-harness detail

## Capability Source

Read `.ai-harness/activation.md` first.
Use `.ai-harness/commands/` and `.ai-harness/prompt-templates/` for command behavior.
Use `.claude/rules/` or `.cursor/rules/` for path-scoped guardrails when the active files match.

## Provider Capabilities

| Capability | Status |
|---|---|
| Slash commands | fallback only |
| Workers/subagents | rules-based |
| Lifecycle hooks | manual setup |
| Path-scoped rules | native |

## Forbidden

- Implementing without a clear goal and approved plan
- Shipping without evidence in `VERIFY.md`
- Writing secrets or private business data into `.harness/`
- Continuing after a blocking question
- Inventing provider capabilities that this repo does not support
